    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Deep, open baskets of varying form intended primarily for gathering or transporting eggs; used especially with reference to those with rib-type construction.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
